        'Invisible hardware is the strict industry standard for these luxury installations. Underground motors ensure the classic lines of the entrance remain totally uninterrupted by visible machinery. Because Aldbury is surrounded by woodland, local technicians take great care to integrate self-cleaning drainage systems beneath these subterranean units, preventing wet autumn leaf fall from clogging the boxes and damaging the sophisticated electronic control boards.',
        'CCTV integrations elevate the security profile of these secluded properties. High-definition video intercoms are mounted discreetly at the entrance, capturing clear footage of every visitor. This visual feed is instantly transmitted to dedicated touchscreens inside the house or securely routed to the homeowner\'s smartphone. This allows Aldbury residents to maintain absolute control over their boundary, blending historical elegance with cutting-edge security.',
