        'Highway constraints often mean driveways are awkwardly shaped or tightly squeezed against the road. A mass-produced gate simply cannot accommodate these spatial quirks safely. Bespoke fabrication ensures the timber panels are crafted to the exact dimensions of your unique entrance. The local maker will tailor the sweeping top rails and bracing to ensure the gate operates flawlessly, providing a permanent, perfectly fitted solution that catalogue products cannot rival.',
