        'Galvanic protection acts as an invisible shield for these high-value installations. A luxury gate is completely worthless if it bleeds rust stains onto an immaculate resin driveway. To prevent this, elite fabricators mandate hot-dip galvanising. This intense chemical bonding process ensures the raw steel is never exposed to the elements. Protected by a sacrificial zinc layer and a baked-on powder coat, the structure guarantees decades of flawless performance.',
